4. CONTRIBUTIONS
==========================================================================

By submitting any contribution to the WolfStack source tree (whether via
pull request, patch, or any other channel), you agree that:

  (a) The contribution is your original work, or you have the right to
      submit it under the terms of this licence; and

  (b) You grant Wolf Software Systems Ltd a perpetual, worldwide, non-
      exclusive, royalty-free licence to use, modify, publish, and
      sublicense your contribution under both Section 2 (PolyForm
      Noncommercial) and Section 3 (commercial licence) above.

A short Contributor Licence Agreement may be required for non-trivial
contributions; see https://wolfstack.org/licensing.php for details.


